<h2 id="sw-cs---petersons-algorithm">S/Wì  CS ë¬¸ì œ í•´ê²°: Petersonâ€™s Algorithm</h2>
<h3 id="petersons-algorithm-">Petersonâ€™s Algorithm ì´ë€?</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>S/Wì  í•´ê²° ë°©ë²•ì´ë‹¤.</strong></li>
